<div class="content-wrapper">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="title"><h1>HAPPENING NOW</h1></div>
        <div class="row-fluid" id="status">
            <div>
                <span class="icon-active-members"></span><strong><%= @stats['members'] %></strong>ACTIVE MEMBERS
            </div>
            <div>
                <span class="icon-competing-today"></span><strong><%= @stats['competing'] %></strong>COMPETING TODAY
            </div>
            <div>
                <span class="icon-available-prize-money"></span><strong><%= number_to_currency(@stats['money_up_for_grabs'], :precision => 0) %></strong>AVAILABLE PRIZE MONEY
            </div>
            <div>
                <span class="active-challenges"></span><strong><%= @stats['challenges_open'] %></strong>ACTIVE CHALLENGES
            </div>
            <div>
                <span class="counteries-working"></span><strong><%= @stats['countries_working'] %></strong>COUNTRIES WORKING
            </div>
        </div>
        <br/>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span6">
                <div class="title"><h1>FEATURED CHALLENGE</h1></div>
                <%= link_to "#{number_to_currency(@featured_challenge.total_prize_money, :precision => 0)} - #{@featured_challenge.name}", challenge_path(@featured_challenge) %>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <p>
                    <% @featured_challenge.challenge_prizes.each do |prize| %>
                    <%= prize.place %> Place <strong><%= prize.prize %></strong><br/>
                    <% end %>
                </p>
                <p>Due in 36h 2m | Ends December 20, 2012 at 7:30 PM<br/>
                    16 members participating, 9 registered
                </p>
                <p>Tags: <a href="#">Salesforce</a> | <a href="#">jQuery Mobile</a> | <a href="#">Android</a> | <a href="#">QuickQuizzes</a></p>
            </div>
            <div class="span6">
                <div class="title"><h1>ACTIVE CHALLENGES</h1></div>
                <% @open_challenges[1..3].each do |challenge| %>
                <%= link_to "#{number_to_currency(challenge.total_prize_money, :precision => 0)} - #{challenge.name}", challenge_path(challenge) %>
                <p>due in 4h 10m | 8 members participating, 5 registered</p>
                <% end %>
                <%= link_to "View All Active Challenges", challenges_path %>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br/>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span6">
                <div class="title"><h1>FEATURED MEMBER</h1></div>
                <div class="placement well">
                    <%= image_tag(@stats['featured_member_pic'], :width => '82x82', :class => 'pull-left photo') %>
                    <%= link_to @stats['featured_member_username'], member_path(@stats['featured_member_username']) %>
                    Challenge Wins: <strong><%= @stats['featured_member_wins'].to_i %></strong><br/>
                    Active Challenges: <strong><%= @stats['featured_member_active'].to_i %></strong>
                    <table class="type featured"><tr><td><%= number_to_currency(@stats['featured_member_money'], :precision => 0) %></td></tr></table>
                </div>

                <p>Quisque luctus neque id mi pretium faucibus. Integer ipsum sem, luctus ut tempus vel, eleifend a arcu. <a href="#">Morbi pretium</a>, nulla ut porta vestibulum, turpis enim venenatis massa, id volutpat velit metus non urna.</p>
                <p>Etiam placerat nisi eu arcu pretium at <a href="#">venenatis lectus vestibulum</a>. Cras gravida massa a nibh condimentum viverra. Vestibulum commodo nisi nec felis rhoncus id porttitor orci eleifend. Aenean facilisis quam ut lectus lobortis euismod.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="span6">
                <div class="title"><h1>LEADERBOARD</h1></div>
                <div class="placement well">
                    <%= image_tag(@leaderboard.first['profile_pic'], :width => '82x82', :class => 'pull-left photo') %>
                    <%= link_to @leaderboard.first['username'], member_path(@leaderboard.first['username']) %>
                    <%= @leaderboard.first['country'] %><br/><%= number_to_currency(@leaderboard.first['total_money'], :precision => 0) %>
